{"tid":2353764,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[港台電視31] 新導演放映室2021 1月10日起 逢星期日晚10點","createTime":"2021-01-05T04:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T15:52:15.000Z","uid":121275,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bb1077ed42bed2b607b1cd23678a9b6c17ab4769","tid":2353764,"uid":121275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dq7QyQ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDq7QyQ3.jpg&h=d77f1ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">新導演放映室2021</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n這是一個外判戲劇計劃，特別為首次執導電視單元劇的新導演而設，題材、類型不限，好讓躍躍欲試的新導演盡情發揮創意。<br />\n<br />\n播出日期: 2021年1月10日起，逢星期日晚10點<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/newtalentdrama2021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fnewtalentdrama2021&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuObXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=2663a567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/newtalentdrama2021</a>"},{"pid":"b3824dcc2d6b23f4d2751305229d5c8ce103dd59","tid":2353764,"uid":121275,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:00:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">無名屍<br />\n10/01/2021</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n面對重大的利益衝突時，人會願意作出犧牲，還是想盡辦法保護自己？<br />\n<br />\n廣告公司的製片楚悠在拍攝前一晚再一次到廢校檢查，確保場地沒有問題，豈料今次碰上了在該處過夜的露宿者。露宿者想對楚悠有不軌企圖，幸好楚悠成功逃脫，但卻在掙扎期間不小心將露宿者打死。<br />\n<br />\n面對著這突如其來的事情，楚悠會作出甚麼決定&hellip;？<br />\n<br />\n主演:吳海昕 岑珈其 黃寶漳<br />\n編導:古翔<br />\n<br />\n播出時間：<br />\n2021年1月10日晚上10點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MC1JWU7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMC1JWU7.jpg&h=f4d4367b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3YVrae8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3YVrae8.jpg&h=07e71f9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0OHs1P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-s