<br />\n<br />\n廣告公司的製片楚悠在拍攝前一晚再一次到廢校檢查，確保場地沒有問題，豈料今次碰上了在該處過夜的露宿者。露宿者想對楚悠有不軌企圖，幸好楚悠成功逃脫，但卻在掙扎期間不小心將露宿者打死。<br />\n<br />\n面對著這突如其來的事情，楚悠會作出甚麼決定&hellip;？<br />\n<br />\n主演:吳海昕 岑珈其 黃寶漳<br />\n編導:古翔<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hgF6GFFVjqc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhgF6GFFVjqc&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuObXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=30e27cbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hgF6GFFVjqc</a>"},{"pid":"814397c9795e5acd21c61b57c4ac0d4567a43090","tid":2353764,"uid":36481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T18:34:24.000Z","msg":"哩集好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估佢唔到<br />\n巴西龜個樣咁正氣都可以咁仆街"},{"pid":"1aeb060a5668405b3a0490c951e88db907b895bf","tid":2353764,"uid":74646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:49:59.000Z","msg":"好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead9df219373bec7af43bf0cfb09c90f8d6ababa","tid":2353764,"uid":121275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">鵝澗小人<br />\n17/01/2021</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣「鵝頸橋」的橋底一直是民間巫術「打小人」的集中地。<br />\n<br />\n那裡聚集一眾「神婆」替人消災解困，何姑就是其中一位。一天，一對母子前來找她。充滿怨氣的母親拿出相片，命何姑要以最惡毒的言詞「打死」相中的負心漢。雖然何姑警告她這樣會折福折壽，但母親仍然堅持。<br />\n<br />\n翌日，何姑發現那母親竟意外死去。生還的兒子來到橋下，要求何姑施法把其母起死回生&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n主演:余俏瑩、徐嘉謙<br />\n編劇:莊玉琳、潘皜暉<br />\n導演:潘皜暉<br />\n<br />\n播出時間：<br />\n2021年1月17日晚上10點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8kTewE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8kTewE.png&h=9c8b636e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLzQgK0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLzQgK0.png&h=aa304797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XYz45Dn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXYz45Dn.png&h=2c65ac01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x4LsiYo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4LsiYo.png&h=9eb4320f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCUXGbK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCUXGbK.png&h=3a44f782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/newtalentdrama2021/episode/721816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fnewtalentdrama2021%2Fepisode%2F721816&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuObXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=051ae5a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/newtalentdrama2021/episode/721816</a>"},{"pid":"c88d344e5c68ea79316aa3f67899e774dd55fcc6","tid":2353764,"uid":121275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T12:00:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">新導演放映室2021<br />\n《鵝澗小人》</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣「鵝頸橋」的橋底一直是民間巫術「打小人」的集中地。<br />\n那裡聚集一眾「神婆」替人消災解困，何姑就是其中一位。一天，一對母子前來找她。充滿怨氣的母親拿出相片，命何姑要以最惡毒的言詞「打死」相中的負心漢。雖然何姑警告她這樣會折福折壽，但母親仍然堅持。<br />\n翌日，何姑發現那母親竟意外死去。生還的兒子來到橋下，要求何姑施法把其母起死回生&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n主演: 余俏瑩、徐嘉謙<br />\n編劇: 莊玉琳、潘皜暉<br />\n導演: 潘皜暉<br />\n----<br />\n1月17日晚10點<br />\n港台電視31<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/newtalentdrama/videos/801898687203439/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnewtalentdrama%2Fvideos%2F801898687203439%2F&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuObXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=804b96cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/newtalentdrama/videos/801898687203439/</a>"},{"pid":"3ed07be95bf1c3fc2e39a5f9afa57aa30b62b573","tid":2353764,"uid":121275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">新導演放映室2021 -《鵝澗小人》<br />\n<br />\n今晚10點<br />\n港台電視31</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SSvTKmX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http